Package: RegressionHelper
Type: Package
Title: Basic Regression Analysis Functions
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Paul Ibzhan JB Cre and Aut
Maintainer: Paul Ibzhan JB <paulibzhansjit@Gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive package that offers essential regression functions,
    including simple linear regression, multiple linear regression, polynomial 
    regression, stepwise regression, and generalized linear models. All functions 
    are implemented using only base R, making them lightweight and easy to use 
    for data analysts and researchers.
